CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 27, 1958, page 23, reads: "Dandy Duffers Winners - Eight members of the Dandy Duffers Golf Club had something to smile about last Sunday at the Flamingo Hotel, as they received trophies at the organization's annual Awards Night ceremonies. Receiving trophies are, left to right, front row: Harry T. Irvin, Harding A. Smith, Henry Morgan and Everett Utterback. Back row: Jackson Wright, Orville Smith, Jack Kelly and Roscoe Young. Taking part in presentation of the trophies was Mrs. Daryl C. Chapman, far right. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Eight men and a woman with Dandy Duffer trophies in bar or restaurant, Flamingo Club
